sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant CLI as rhai-cli<br/>(kubectl-odh)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OLM as OLM API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GitHub as odh-gitops<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem

    Note over Admin,FS: Flow 1: Upgrade Readiness Lint (rhai-cli lint --target-version 3.x)

    Admin->>CLI: rhai-cli lint --target-version 3.0
    activate CLI

    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET DataScienceCluster (singleton)<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSC spec + status

    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET DSCInitialization (singleton)<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSCI spec (applications namespace)

    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST Subscriptions, CSVs<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: OLM operator versions

    par Dependency Checks (3 checks)
        CLI->>K8sAPI: GET cert-manager CRD
        CLI->>K8sAPI: GET ClusterVersion
        CLI->>K8sAPI: GET ServiceMesh resources
    end

    par Platform Checks (2 checks)
        CLI->>K8sAPI: Validate DSC readiness
        CLI->>K8sAPI: Validate DSCI readiness
    end

    par Component Checks (11 checks)
        CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST KServe configs, Kuadrant, Authorino
        CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST Kueue resources, RHBOK status
        CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST Dashboard profiles, Ray, Training
    end

    par Workload Checks (21 checks)
        CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST Notebooks (all namespaces)
        CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST InferenceServices (all namespaces)
        CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST RayClusters, PyTorchJobs
        CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST DSPAs, ClusterQueues, LocalQueues
        CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST GuardrailsOrchestrators
        CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST LlamaStackDistributions
    end

    CLI-->>Admin: Diagnostic Results Table<br/>(Prohibited / Blocking / Advisory / None)
    deactivate CLI

    Note over Admin,FS: Flow 2: Workload Backup (rhai-cli backup notebooks)

    Admin->>CLI: rhai-cli backup notebooks -o ./backups
    activate CLI

    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST Notebooks (discovery)<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Notebook resources

    loop For each Notebook
        CLI->>K8sAPI: GET referenced ConfigMaps<br/>Bearer Token
        CLI->>K8sAPI: GET referenced Secrets<br/>Bearer Token
        CLI->>K8sAPI: GET referenced PVCs<br/>Bearer Token
    end

    CLI->>FS: Write YAML files<br/>(metadata stripped:<br/>uid, resourceVersion, status)

    CLI-->>Admin: Backup complete: N resources written
    deactivate CLI

    Note over Admin,FS: Flow 3: Kueue Migration (rhai-cli migrate run kueue-rhbok)

    Admin->>CLI: rhai-cli migrate run kueue-rhbok
    activate CLI

    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST ClusterQueues (backup)<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET kueue ConfigMap (backup)<br/>Bearer Token
    CLI->>FS: Write backup YAML files

    CLI->>K8sAPI: CREATE Subscription<br/>(kueue-operator, stable-v1.1)<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+

    loop Poll until CSV Succeeded
        CLI->>K8sAPI: GET ClusterServiceVersion<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>CLI: CSV phase (Installing → Succeeded)
    end

    CLI->>K8sAPI: PATCH DataScienceCluster<br/>(set Kueue: Unmanaged)<br/>MergePatch, Bearer Token

    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST ClusterQueues (verify preserved)<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: ClusterQueues intact

    CLI-->>Admin: Migration complete:<br/>RHBOK installed, DSC patched,<br/>resources preserved
    deactivate CLI
